text: Oh Jin-hyek (born 15 August 1981) is a South Korean archer. Oh competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Oh Jin-HyeokJin Hyek OH ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for South Korea Category:Olympic bronze medalists for South Korea
